# UI stack (strict)

Do **not** introduce, suggest, install, or import third-party UI component libraries, CSS-in-JS frameworks, or icon packs outside this stack.

## Approved

- **Tailwind CSS** — all styling and utilities.
- **Shadcn UI** — all pre-built components (`components/ui/*`).
- **Radix UI** — only as headless primitives underlying Shadcn (do not add Radix for ad-hoc use outside existing patterns).
- **Lucide React** — all icons.

## Banned

- Component kits: Material UI (MUI), Chakra, Ant Design, Bootstrap, Mantine, NextUI, etc.
- CSS-in-JS: styled-components, Emotion, CSS Modules (unless already required by an approved tool).
- Other icon sets: Heroicons, Font Awesome, etc.

## When building UI

- Compose with **Tailwind** and existing **Shadcn** pieces in `components/ui/`.
- If a Shadcn primitive is missing, add it with: `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` (use the project’s documented command if different).
- **Input height**: default form controls use **`h-11`** via `components/ui/input.tsx`; keep selects and native `<select>` at the same visual height unless there is a documented exception.
